<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6389562>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Bronchocela hayeki in life (UIMZ 0243, adult male): (A) lateral view of the full body, (B) dorsal head, (C) lateral head, (D) ventral head, and (E) secondary forest habitat collected from near the type locality." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6389562/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6389556>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Current distribution map showing the collection/observation localities of Bronchocela hayeki (yellow) on Sumatra Island, its sympatric congener, B. cristatella sensu lato (blue) and allopatric congener B. jubata sensu lato (red) also indicated on the map; sympatric localities filled partially" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6389556/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

